Beautiful 5 bedroom, 2 full , 3/4 and 2 1/4 bath home located in Cherry Creek School District. Main level includes a large living room, half-bath, dining area and a spacious kitchen with lots of cabinets, newer stove and refrigerator, range hood will replace with white over the range microwave, Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms and two additional baths. Large loft, Large master bedroom comfortably fits a king sized bed and includes two walk-in closets. In the basement you will find two large bedrooms, custom 3/4 bath, storage space. Attached 2-car garage. large backyard with nice green view. Walking distance to the neighborhood park. Great location.

Beautiful 5-bedroom House in the Saddle Rock Area!! Welcome to your new home in the highly sought-after Saddle Rock area, just around the corner from Eaglecrest High School! This 5 bed, 4 bath beauty boasts 3056 sq. ft. of luxurious living space. Step inside to be greeted by a versatile office/flex space and newly refinished hardwood floors throughout the main level. The heart of the home is the expansive kitchen, complete with pristine granite countertops, large granite center island, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast nook/dining room that flows seamlessly into the family room, making it perfect for family gatherings. Step outside to the large deck, perfect for grilling and long wrap around astroturf backyard, ideal for outdoor entertaining. Upstairs, you'll find three well-appointed bedrooms, including a spacious primary en suite with a five-piece bath for your relaxation. The newly finished basement offers even more living space, with a generous living area and a private bedroom with an en suite bathroom, perfect for guests or a teenager looking for their own retreat. Don't miss this opportunity to make this stunning house your new home sweet home! Contact us today to schedule a showing. Other amenities include a covered front porch, deep attached two-car garage, ceiling fan in every bedroom, washer and dryer. A/C. minimum 12-month lease. Dogs are O.K. Security Deposit is $3600. Pet rent $45/mo. Pet deposit is $300 and refundable. Available January 17th. Income required is 2 times the rent. Highly rated Cherry Creek Schools. 10 Min from Southlands Mall and Saddle Rock Golf Course. 5 Min from E-470. Don't miss this wonderful opportunity! Text for Showings.
